  "doc_id": "15410",
  "text": "In connection with the Z 4 parafermion state, there are several other related non-Abelian trial states in the bilayer quantum Hall system at ν = n + 2/3 with n being the filled Landau level index. These trial states include the intralayer Pfaffian state [CITATION_1] , the interlayer Pfaffian state [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , the Fibonacci state [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] , and the Bonderson-Slingerland state [CITATION_6] .",
